Whew. Almost ten years of “recreatingnicole”, or if you’re a super OG follower “sleevednicole”
If you’ve been around the whole time, hey hi hello - what a wild ride it’s been, huh?
Obviously weight loss being the main topic of my page to start, but the crazy life changes that have occurred throughout documenting my life on this page are insane. But if you’re new here, here’s a super quick recap of some major highlights. 
2014- I lost 90lbs with VSG, had my gallbladder removed due to weight loss, moved from Massachusetts to Washington, had a revision to gastric bypass in 2017, lost another 90lbs (180 total), moved back to Massachusetts, mentally ill af lol, had a tummy tuck + back lift in Tijuana, moved to houston Texas, had my arms-boobs-thighs done, pandemic hit, moved back to Seattle, opened up a business while simultaneously going off the fucking rails, my mental health plummeted- I completely gave up on my body, met my now husband, got my mental health in check, grew my business, got pregnant 3 months prior to our wedding, had a significantly difficult pregnancy, had the most precious baby, postpartum hit me like a ton of bricks, and now here we areeeeeee. 
I told you, welcome to the shit show ✨
Oversharing has always been my thing - but reality is that posting my goals and progress keeps me motivated and inspired. And I’d like to think that the 80,000+ of you must be somewhat interested in that too! 
This page isn’t 100% weight loss related. It’s just my life. Learning balance, loving my life while working on myself + health. 
I am the happiest and healthiest mentally I have been in 10 years, and I’m stoked to have my physical body match that energy 
All signed up with @sarahf_fitwithme @teamfitwithme to assist me with my new goals!
I can’t wait to lose this regain, and to see where we are 6 months from now. 💖
